    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .a {font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Batang'; font-size: 14pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-family: 'Batang'; font-size: 14pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">ДАЛОЛАТНОМА</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">(</span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#10}Топширилаётган товар моддий бойлик (ускуна, асосий восита)нинг номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold;\">ни топшириш ва қабул қилиш тўғрисида</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">)</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"\">{#2}Далолатнома тузилган сана</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"\">{#3}Далолатнома тузилган жой</span></p>\n<p></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ташкилотнинг номи ва уни ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Буйруқ қабул қилган раҳбарнинг лавозими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">и<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Буйруқ қабул қилган раҳбарнинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#14}Буйруқ қабул қилинган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">кунидаги </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Буйруқ рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-сонли буйруғига асосан </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Қабул қилувчи шахснинг лавозими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Қабул қилувчи шахснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ташкилотнинг номи ва уни ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> балансидаги </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Товар моддий бойлик (ускуна, асосий восита) ишлаб чиқарилган йили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда ишлаб чиқарилган, </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Товар моддий бойлик (ускуна, асосий восита)нинг рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> рақамли </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Товар моддий бойлик (ускуна, асосий восита) нинг русуми</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> русумли </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#19}Товар моддий бойлик (ускуна, асосий восита)нинг номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> унинг моддий жавобгарлиги остида бириктирилиши белгиланган.</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Шунга кўра, корхона балансидаги </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Товар моддий бойлик (ускуна, асосий восита) ишлаб чиқарилган йили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда ишлаб чиқарилган, </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Товар моддий бойлик (ускуна, асосий восита)нинг рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> рақамли </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Товар моддий бойлик (ускуна, асосий восита) нинг русуми</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> русумли </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#19}Товар моддий бойлик (ускуна, асосий восита)нинг номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Далолатнома тузилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> куни </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Топширувчи шахснинг лавозими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Топширувчи шахснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Қабул қилувчи шахснинг лавозими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Қабул қилувчи шахснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га топширилди, </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Қабул қилувчи шахснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> эса қабул қилиб олди.</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Топширувчи:</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Топширувчи шахснинг лавозими</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class